[Cite as 09/11/2003 Case Announcements, 2003-0hio-4781.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

September 11, 2003

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2003-0350. State v. Reine.

Montgomery App. No. 19157, 2003-0hio-50. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Montgomery County. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to dismiss,

It is ordered by the court that the motion to dismiss be, and hereby is, sustained.

It is further ordered by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and O’Connor, JJ., concur. Lundberg Stratton and O’Donnell, JJ., dissent.
